\item Symmetric Difference (SD): (2 \emph{d} + \emph{r1} + \emph{r2}) / (2 \emph{d} + 2 \emph{s} + \emph{r1} + \emph{r2})
}

The total distinctly resolved quartets or partitions (Day 1986):
